<topic id="word-line-actions">
  <title>Word/Line Editor Actions</title><prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Text Editing Mode<indexterm>word/line editor actions</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> editor implements the following actions:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><uicontrol>
          <shortcut>(Ctrl+Delete (Meta+Delete on Mac))</shortcut></uicontrol> - deletes the next
        word;</li>
      <li><uicontrol>
          <shortcut>(Ctrl+Backspace (Meta+Backspace on Mac))</shortcut></uicontrol> - deletes the
        previous word;</li>
      <li><uicontrol>
          <shortcut>(Ctrl+W (Meta+W on Mac))</shortcut></uicontrol> - cuts the previous word;</li>
      <li><uicontrol>
          <shortcut>(Ctrl+K (Meta+K on Mac))</shortcut></uicontrol> - cuts to end of line.</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
